import { DndProvider, useDrag, useDrop } from 'react-dnd'; import { HTML5Backend } from 'react-dnd-html5-backend'; import { useState } from 'react'; import './Board.css'; import Hexagon from './Hexagon'; import Champion from './Champion'; function Board() { const [positions, setPositions] = useState({ ashe: {x: 350, y: 250}, // default bottom right garen: {x: 50, y: 50} // default top left }); const handleDragStart = (id) => { // Save initial position } const handleDragEnd = (id, dropResult) => { // Check valid hexagon drop // Update positions state // Reset old hexagon } return ( handleDragStart('ashe')} onDragEnd={handleDragEnd} />
); } export default Board;
